## Part 4 – Auto-update and completion behavior

- When new rules/skills are provided, append/update rule files; suggest improvements and version (e.g. v1.3).
- **Always** test generated code (pytest, go test, bats) before marking complete.
- Explain changes and suggest tests/CI integration.

