## Part 7 – UI verification (before marking UI work complete)

- **Run validation** (app must be running at http://localhost:3000):  
  `cd zeroops && yarn validate:ui`
- **All routes must pass;** fix any failures before marking done.
- Optional: `yarn test:e2e` for Playwright (app must be running).
- **Do not** mark UI work complete until `yarn validate:ui` passes and affected pages render correctly (sidebar, filters, view toggle as expected).  
- See routes: `/`, `/catalog`, `/catalog/users`, `/api-docs`, `/create`, `/search`.

