## Part 10 – Git commit messages

- When pushing code to GitHub, **do not include "cursor-bot" (or "Cursor Bot", "cursor bot") in the commit message.**
- **Do not add the trailer `Made-with: Cursor` (or any "Made-with" / tool trailer) to commit messages.**
- Use clear, conventional commit messages (e.g. feat:, fix:, docs:) without tool or bot names in the message body or subject.

